overview.en: ALC is to solve the problem of revenue security between the platform and users for the majority of users. In the era of big data, everyone can have a second career. How can we guarantee our own revenue without the restriction of labor contract? ALC can guarantee the revenue security of every user based on the support of blockchain Technology.
overview.zh: ALC是为广大用户解决平台与用户之间的收益安全问题，在大数据时代，每一个人都可以拥有第二职业，在没有劳动合同约束下，我们如何保障自己的收益，ALC基于区块链技术的支持，可以保障每一位用户的收益安全。
